[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to burn.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 10% chance to burn the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Fire Punch is a special attack in RBY and its users normally lack STAB, so unless you are using it on a tradeback Alakazam to cover Exeggutor better, you won't use this move.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/flamethrower">Flamethrower</a> is a stronger alternative with 95 Base Power and 100% accuracy.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/fire_blast">Fire Blast</a> is a stronger alternative with 120 Base Power and 30% chance to burn, albeit less accuracy.</p>